headline: How Is Alexandria Real Estate’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Real Estate Stocks?
summary: Alexandria Real Estate has lagged behind the broader Real Estate sector over the past year; however, analysts maintain a cautiously optimistic outlook on the stock’s future performance.
